					description = <"*">
					comment = <"(((((((Gait + Stance) + Sitting) + Speech Disturbance) + Finger chase-mean of both sides) + Nose-finger test-mean of both sides) + Fast alternating hand movements-mean of both sides) + Heel-shin slide-mean of both sides) ">
